(67516, 132418, 0, 1, 'Planck 普朗克 (Orginal Mix)', 'Eds - Planck 普朗克 (Orginal Mix) 第六首單曲來了！我這次靈感來至一艘太空船名為Planck，可能是最近科幻片看多了吧，這次還是走偏Progressive house的元素在裡面，做來做去我還是挺愛這類型的風格，過一陣子會開始做一些多點Vocal的東西，希望大家會喜歡囉！繼續支持EDM類型的音樂在亞洲發展！如果覺得不錯～請記得到我的粉絲團DJEdsTaiwan按個讚了，我會持續的創作下去！\n\nEds - Planck Planck (Orginal Mix)of my sixth single is released! The inspiration came from a spaceship called the Planck, which was perhaps influenced by the excessive amount of science fiction films I''ve watched recently. This track has the element of progressive house in it, which I find to have passion for after my other attempts, from now on I will have more vocals in my tracks, and I hope you guys like it! Please support EDM in Asia! If you like the track remember to like my fan page DJEdsTaiwan, and I will continue to go creative! Thanks!\n\nFacebook\nwww.facebook.com/DJEds\n\nFanpage\nwww.facebook.com/DJEdsTaiwan\n\nYoutube\nwww.youtube.com/TaiwanDjEds\n\nSoundcloud\n@djeds\n\nMixCloud\nwww.mixcloud.com/DJEds\n\nMixcrate\nwww.mixcrate.com/djeds\n\n個人聯絡信箱：\n\ndj.eds@hotmail.com', '2013-08-08 00:00:00', 2013, 30, 1, 3, '', '', 246, '', 'Eds', '', 'Eds', 'Eds', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-10-28 02:32:22', '2015-03-12 14:02:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
