(67518, 132418, 0, 1, 'Don''t Give Up 別放棄 (Orginal Mix)', '大家好！我是Eds，Don''t Give Up 別放棄 (Original Mix) 是我今年最期待發的一首作品，可能也是最完整的一首，我也醞釀了很久盡量讓他最完美的呈現出來，我想我這次想要表達的是傳撥愛是有很多種不同的方式，而我就是使用這種方式表達，希望大家跟我一樣別放棄，感謝你們支持我！Love you guys\n\nHey what''s up Edison here! My new single Don''t Give Up (Original Mix) which is also the song I''m most excited for this year is finally released! This track is by far the most complete and took me the longest to try to make it perfect for you guys. My inspiration of the track came from the thought of ways to show love, and writing is my way express it. Hope you guys don''t give up on the things you love, and we could go through the tough times together. Thank you guys for the support, much appreciation! Love u guys\n\nFacebook \nwww.facebook.com/DJEds\n\nFanpage \nwww.facebook.com/DJEdsTaiwan\n\nYoutube \nwww.youtube.com/TaiwanDjEds\n\nSoundcloud\n@djeds\n\nMixCloud \nwww.mixcloud.com/DJEds\n\nMixcrate \nwww.mixcrate.com/djeds\n\n個人聯絡信箱：\ndj.eds@hotmail.com', '2013-09-01 00:00:00', 2013, 30, 1, 3, 'I remember what you did for me\n\nFeeling so [broke] and you set me free\n\nIf I search I never find\n\nThe kind of love that''s worth my time\n\nWhy don''t people appreciate\n\nIt''s the routine here so little love\n \nWhat the world need now is love\n\nToo many roads we must run\n\nToo many hopes come undone\n\nTry as hard as you must\n\nYou''ll have a chance don''t give up\n\nCould not imagine what my life would be\n\nIf you haven''t seen the light in me\n\nIn every wind peace welcome in\n\nAnd time goes by\n\nWhy don''t people understand\n\nThe gift of love that is a [pain]  It''s the power for you to decide\n\nThat we must keep love alive\n\nToo many roads we must run\n\nToo many hopes come undone\n\nTry as hard as you must\n\nYou''ll have a chance don''t give up\n\nIt''s a new sensation blowing in my mind\n\nGonna be there for you till the end of time', '', 343, '', 'Eds', '', 'Eds', 'Eds Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-10-28 02:40:23', '2015-03-12 1